OL,6,FITV Channel's Michael Maitland-Jones
OL,7,Fgot up close with the island's iconic
OL,8,Ftapestry...
OL,10,F's millennium tapestry will be moved
OL,11,Ffrom its current home at The Whittaker
OL,12,FGallery in St James later this year.
OL,14,FThe work of art depicts a thousand
OL,15,Fyears of Guernsey - from when the
OL,16,Fisland came under the rule of William
OL,17,Fthe Conqueror and right up to the
OL,18,Foccupation.
