OL,6,FIan Hunter, a tapestry trustee, said:
OL,7,F"For me, the tapestry is a history of
OL,8,Fthe island in easily digestible panels
OL,9,F- anybody can come in here and get an
OL,10,Fidea of what the history of the island
OL,11,Fis".
OL,13,FThe owners of the gallery in St James
OL,14,Fneeded to use the space for other
OL,15,Fevent, causing concerns that it might
OL,16,Fhave to be moved into storage or off-
OL,17,Fisland.
